"Trail of legends"- new freeware scenario for Macintosh Wolfenstein 3d.
To install it, just put scenario file into Level folder.
  Made with WolfEdit 2.0.4. and Photoshop 1.0
Level design: Marchenco Andrey
Artist: Marchenco Andrey
Testers: Artem Strigyn
              Kazaev Alexander
              Semeyonov Ilya
  
Moscow, Russia.

This scenario is absolutely free, so you can copy it, give to your friends... and do what you want with it.

Thank You for playing!!!